---
---

<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Request Software - Berbagi Aplikasi</title>
    
    <script src="https://identity.netlify.com/v1/netlify-identity-widget.js"></script>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: #f8fafc; margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #334155; }
        .navbar { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e3a8a 100%); padding: 15px 40px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 100; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.2); }
        .brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; text-decoration: none; }
        .brand-logo { width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 8px; object-fit: contain; background-color: white; padding: 2px;}
        .brand-text { margin: 0; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; color: #ffffff; }
        .nav-menu { display: flex; gap: 15px; align-items: center; }
        .nav-link { text-decoration: none; color: #cbd5e1; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 12px; transition: all 0.3s; }
        .nav-link:hover { background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); color: #ffffff; }
        .nav-btn-special { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14b8a6, #0d9488); color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 12px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; font-size: 14px; box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(20, 184, 166, 0.4);}
        
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 60px auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        .form-box { background-color: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.05); border: 1px solid #f1f5f9;}
        .page-title { margin-top: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; color: #0f172a; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 10px;}
        .page-desc { text-align: center; color: #64748b; margin-bottom: 30px; line-height: 1.6;}
        
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .form-label { display: block; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; color: #334155; font-size: 14px;}
        .form-input { width: 100%; padding: 12px 15px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 10px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box; transition: all 0.3s;}
        .form-input:focus { outline: none; border-color: #3b82f6; box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1); }
        textarea.form-input { resize: vertical; min-height: 120px; }
        
        .btn-submit { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #1d4ed8); color: white; border: none; padding: 14px 24px; border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; width: 100%; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.3s; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;}
        .btn-submit:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(37,99,235,0.2); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
            <img src="/logo.png" alt="Logo" class="brand-logo" onerror="this.src='https://placehold.co/40x40/2563eb/white?text=BA'">
            <h1 class="brand-text">Berbagi Aplikasi</h1>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-menu">
            <a href="/request" class="nav-btn-special">📝 Request Software</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="form-box">
            <h1 class="page-title">Request Software</h1>
            <p class="page-desc">Tidak menemukan aplikasi yang kamu cari? Beritahu kami aplikasi apa yang kamu butuhkan, dan kami akan berusaha menyediakannya untukmu!</p>
            
            <form name="request-software" method="POST" data-netlify="true">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label" for="nama">Nama Kamu</label>
                    <input type="text" id="nama" name="nama" class="form-input" placeholder="Misal: Budi" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label" for="nama_software">Nama Software yang Direquest</label>
                    <input type="text" id="nama_software" name="nama_software" class="form-input" placeholder="Misal: CorelDraw 2024" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="form-label" for="alasan">Pesan Tambahan (Opsional)</label>
                    <textarea id="alasan" name="pesan" class="form-input" placeholder="Tambahkan detail versi, sistem operasi, atau link referensi jika ada..."></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit">Kirim Request 🚀</button>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>